      <P></P>
      <P><STRONG><EM>see also:</EM></STRONG></P>
      <UL>
        <UL>
          <LI><A=20
          =
href=3D"http://orcmid.com/blog/2008/02/interoperability-by-design.asp">In=
teroperability=20
          by Design</A>, <EM>Orcmid's Lair</EM>, 2008-02-26<BR>my =
reaction to=20
          the 2008-02-21 Microsoft announcement of interoperability=20
